      "title": "Sri Lanka schedules power cuts of up to 3 hours for July 23",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka will impose\u00a0power\u00a0cuts\u00a0of up to 3 hours on July 23, Public Utilities\u00a0Commission (PUCSL) Chairman Janaka Ratnayake said.",
        "All areas (ABCDEFGHIJKLPQRSTUVW) will have\u00a0power\u00a0cuts\u00a0of 1 hours and 40 minutes between 10.20 am and 06.00 pm and 1 hour 20 minutes power cuts from 06.00pm to 10.00 pm.",
        "The state-run Ceylon Electricity Board (CEB) said the supply interruption time and restoration time will be varied within 30 minutes as indicated above. (Colombo/ July 23/2022)"
      ],
